#. module: bike_leasing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_leasing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If the stock levels are too low, resupply the materials from the\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                        <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Purchase</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                app by creating a purchase order linked to the right vendor. In the\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                        <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Contact</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                app, you can easily manage all your preferred vendors and don't hesitate to set a warning to remind if there is a minimum amount to get free transport costs."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າລະດັບສິນຄ້າໃນສາງຕໍ່າເກີນໄປ, ໃຫ້ຕື່ມສິນຄ້າຈາກ\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                        <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຈັດຊື້</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                ແອັບ ໂດຍການສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຊື້ທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບຜູ້ສະໜອງທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ໃນ\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                        <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                ແອັບ, ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການຜູ້ສະໜອງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການທັງໝົດໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ ແລະ ຢ່າລັງເລທີ່"
"ຈະຕັ້ງຄຳເຕືອນເພື່ອແຈ້ງໃຫ້ຊາບ ຫາກມີຍອດສັ່ງຊື້ຂັ້ນຕໍ່າເພື່ອໃຫ້ໄດ້ຄ່າຂົນສົ່ງຟຣີ."

